// 單一AcountID(user)對上Product Family(product), rating表示購買次數
val raw_data = Lab2_loaddata.select($"Quotation: Quotation ID",$"Display Quantity",$"Account ID",$"Product: Product Family",$"PRODUCT ID",$"Description")
val user_product = raw_data.select($"Account ID".alias("user"), $"PRODUCT ID".alias("product"),$"Display Quantity".alias("number")).groupBy("user","product").agg(count("number").alias("rating")).toDF() 


/* 將User與product分別配上獨立ID，一出現次數由大到小排序後加上ID
此轉換是為了 CF_ALS 模型格式需求 
user: [Int]
product: [Int]
rating: [Double]
*/
val userIndexer = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("user").setOutputCol("userID").setHandleInvalid("keep")
val indexed = userIndexer.fit(user_product).transform(user_product)
val productIndexer = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("product").setOutputCol("productID").setHandleInvalid("keep")

val whole = productIndexer.fit(indexed).transform(indexed)

val user_mapping = whole.select("user","userID").distinct.toDF()
val product_mapping = whole.select("product","productID").distinct.toDF()
val whole_select_rating = whole.select($"userID".cast("int"),$"productID".cast("int"),$"rating".cast("double"))

//  CF 準備
val unique_product = whole_select_rating.dropDuplicates("productID")
val unique_user = whole_select_rating.dropDuplicates("userID")
val join = unique_user.union(unique_product)
val unique_product_user = join.dropDuplicates()
val test_notyet = whole_select_rating.except(unique_product_user)

val Array(training, test) = test_notyet.randomSplit(Array[Double](0.7, 0.3), seed= 1234L)
val train_final = unique_product_user.union(training)
val test_final = test


val tableRDD = whole_select_rating.rdd.map(r => Rating(
  r.getAs[Int]("userID"), r.getAs[Int]("productID"), r.getAs[Double]("rating")
))

val trainRDD = train_final.rdd.map(r => Rating(
  r.getAs[Int]("userID"), r.getAs[Int]("productID"), r.getAs[Double]("rating")
))

/*

Association rule

*/
val col = raw_data.select("Quotation: Quotation ID", "PRODUCT ID")
val basket = col.groupBy("Quotation: Quotation ID").agg(collect_set("PRODUCT ID").alias("Product_ID")).toDF()
val fpgrowth = new FPGrowth().setItemsCol("Product_ID").setMinSupport(0.001).setMinConfidence(0.5)
val model_fpgrowth = fpgrowth.fit(basket)
model_fpgrowth.transform(basket)
val ifThen = model_fpgrowth.associationRules
ifThen.createOrReplaceTempView("ifThen")
val ifThen_filter = spark.sql("select antecedent, consequent, confidence from ifThen where size(antecedent) < 2 and size(consequent) < 2 order by confidence desc")
